strong language and violent scenes.

00:15.000 --> 00:16.320
Dad?

00:16.320 --> 00:17.760
- Kelly.
- Dad!

00:17.760 --> 00:21.120
It was them Peckham Boys, Dad. They
got me at the lockup down the yard.

00:21.120 --> 00:23.880
Leonard, round up your cousins
and get down there!

00:23.880 --> 00:25.360
- I'm going too, Dad.
- No way.

00:25.360 --> 00:28.080
There was a time when the Lord name
counted for something.

00:28.080 --> 00:30.080
Look at you now. Light him up.

00:30.080 --> 00:32.040
No. Please!

00:33.040 --> 00:36.880
Did your uncle ever mention the name
Ernesto Alvarez to you?

00:36.880 --> 00:38.440
No. Why?

00:38.440 --> 00:40.480
They met around the time
he was killed.

00:40.480 --> 00:42.000
Hola muchacha.

00:48.280 --> 00:50.040
They're fucking Gypsies.

00:50.040 --> 00:52.640
I'll get shot of them when I want.
It's my land.

00:52.640 --> 00:54.360
Let's find these fucking deeds!

00:55.800 --> 00:58.160
See that police officer
you ran into?

00:58.160 --> 00:59.520
Yeah?

01:00.840 --> 01:02.280
He's dead, baby.

01:04.080 --> 01:05.480
It's Cindy.

01:05.480 --> 01:07.960
She's hiding something from us, Kel.

01:07.960 --> 01:10.080
She weren't for me anyway.

01:10.080 --> 01:12.200
I always knew she was a wrong 'un.

