♪ In the middle of our
Our house is... ♪

19:09.880 --> 19:11.960
Who the fuck are those people?

19:11.960 --> 19:13.440
What you doing here?

19:13.440 --> 19:15.320
Sorry, we did knock.

19:15.320 --> 19:18.640
I'm Lola.
And this is my sister Manuela.

19:18.640 --> 19:22.200
- And?
- And we're from a small
Gitano community here

19:22.200 --> 19:24.160
that live on your land.

19:24.160 --> 19:25.560
Our land?

19:25.560 --> 19:27.880
Yes, and as the new landowners,

19:27.880 --> 19:31.200
my father would like to welcome you
to come over for dinner tonight.

19:31.200 --> 19:33.160
And celebrate with our people.

19:33.160 --> 19:36.400
It would be an honour
to have you as our guests.

19:36.400 --> 19:37.680
I don't fucking think so.

19:38.680 --> 19:40.320
Dad, come on.

19:40.320 --> 19:41.800
No, it would...

19:41.800 --> 19:44.600
...it would be our honour.
No, Son, no.

19:44.600 --> 19:46.160
Dad, please.

19:46.160 --> 19:47.880
We'd love to.

19:47.880 --> 19:49.160
Gracias.

19:52.440 --> 19:54.120
A gift.

19:54.120 --> 19:55.400
From your land.

19:55.400 --> 19:56.760
A tradition.

19:59.200 --> 20:01.720
Dad, what have you got to say?

20:01.720 --> 20:03.240
Gracias. Gracias.

20:05.520 --> 20:08.280
We appreciate you coming.
I'll see you out.

20:08.280 --> 20:11.680
Gypsies on our land?
Maybe they have a right to roam.

20:11.680 --> 20:15.040
Well, unless they've got 50 grand,
they can fuck off back there.

20:15.040 --> 20:17.280
- Leonard.
- Fucking hell, Dad.

20:17.280 --> 20:20.440
No, no, no, fuck off, Len.
No, no, no.

20:20.440 --> 20:23.040
Sooner we sell this land
and get home, the better.

20:23.040 --> 20:24.680
I'm going in. It's fucking hot.

20:29.800 --> 20:32.160
What the fuck are you doing
with this anyway?

20:32.160 --> 20:34.040
I heard you just got out of jail.

20:34.040 --> 20:36.160
Yeah. TDA, mate.

20:36.160 --> 20:37.840
I stole a car.

20:37.840 --> 20:40.080
Hardly crime of the fucking century.

20:42.120 --> 20:44.560
How did you wind up in the nick, then?

20:45.760 --> 20:48.040
Look at me... you fool.

20:51.680 --> 20:54.640
I'm not sure how I'm going to
break this one to Ma.

20:56.440 --> 20:59.760
