45:42.480 --> 45:46.200
that you do whatever it takes,
everything in your power,

45:46.200 --> 45:47.880
to make it right again.

45:49.160 --> 45:51.000
Otherwise, you'll grow old alone.

46:17.360 --> 46:18.680
Gene...

46:18.680 --> 46:20.320
...my boy.

46:22.120 --> 46:24.360
You fancy coming for a drive
with me?

46:30.360 --> 46:33.240
I didn't give the best account
of myself last night.

46:33.240 --> 46:36.600
So I was thinking that we could
go back up to the Gitanos and say...

46:37.760 --> 46:40.480
...and say, let's start again.

46:42.480 --> 46:43.880
They trust you.

46:43.880 --> 46:45.520
So do I.

46:46.760 --> 46:48.280
I need you with me.

46:49.600 --> 46:50.920
My general.

46:58.400 --> 46:59.800
Papa...

47:15.560 --> 47:17.480
We're just here to talk.

47:17.480 --> 47:19.400
We've nothing to say to you.

47:19.400 --> 47:20.920
What he did...

47:20.920 --> 47:23.120
...it's unforgiveable, I know that.

47:24.280 --> 47:27.480
But we have a lot more to gain
from friendship than war.

47:27.480 --> 47:29.440
You live on this land.

47:29.440 --> 47:31.440
We own it.

47:31.440 --> 47:34.160
So we need to find a way
to live side by side in peace.

47:37.680 --> 47:39.200
Dad?

47:40.960 --> 47:42.640
What the boy said...

47:42.640 --> 47:44.960
...we need to learn to get on.

47:48.760 --> 47:50.240
I was insulted.

47:50.240 --> 47:52.840
Where I'm from,
a man can't let that slide.

47:54.760 --> 47:56.360
I was protecting my family.

47:56.360 --> 47:57.720
You understand that.

47:59.120 --> 48:01.680
I made a rick, it was a mistake.

48:04.360 --> 48:07.240
I have met... bad men...

48:08.360 --> 48:10.640
...stupid men, arrogant men.

48:11.840 --> 48:14.480
All gentlemen, compared with you.

48:15.560 --> 48:17.520
You say you protect your family.

48:18.600 --> 48:20.560
You know nothing about family!

48:20.560 --> 48:22.760
Even your boy can see that.

48:23.800 --> 48:25.560
You're not a father...

48:25.560 --> 48:27.000
...not a husband!

48:28.480 --> 48:32.400
You'll never build your hotel
on this land.

48:37.800 --> 48:39.080
Please.

48:39.080 --> 48:41.120
I'm sorry.

48:44.480 --> 48:46.240
I need to make this right.

48:47.280 --> 48:50.640
I...truly am sorry.

48:57.840 --> 48:59.600
Get the fuck off my land.

49:07.640 --> 49:09.160
You did really well, Dad.

49:22.160 --> 49:23.560
Here you are.

49:23.560 --> 49:24.680
Hey.

49:27.800 --> 49:29.560
Well, he actually did it.

49:31.080 --> 49:32.720
I'm so proud of you.

49:33.720 --> 49:35.480
